reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I Like them USB Drives very well
reviews.reviewText: At first I thought they weren't even going to fit in my 13-inch mid 2012 MacBook Pro but it works and fits in my MacBook just fine and the storage on the drive is sufficient. I would certainly buy them again and in bulk too (one other thing I do like about them, is the fact that they're so small I can fit two of them in my MacBooks USB slot and usually whenever I have other thumb drives I can only use one since they're usually too big for the other to fit into the neighboring slot.)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Disappointed. Did not work. Will not be recognized in MAC OR PC
reviews.reviewText: I purchased this item with hopes of using to update the navigation in my vehicle. At first it accepted the software update, then when I tried to connect it in my vehicle it was not recognized. I tried to troubleshoot once more on my MAC and I kept getting an error message that it could not be read. I tried using my PC and was met with another error message that the drive was in “write protection” and there was no way of re-formatting. This sucks because now I’m stuck with a useless usb drive. I can’t even reset to original default settings by deleting any information onboard.
